{"tid":1588400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"3M 60926 擋水罩/ 6006 擋水罩 combo p95 or n95","createTime":"2019-09-22T20:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T17:01:43.000Z","uid":325386,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"0667b8dac83361a284bcd30f3cd378de0952f5af","tid":1588400,"uid":325386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T20:11:47.000Z","msg":"唔知道各位有冇遇過要成日出入啲<strong>好多塵好多煙</strong>嘅地方呢，然後<strong>諗住帶mask</strong>，又發現嗰個地方有機會<strong>成日落雨或者有水柱</strong>有機會射到你個面罩? 我哋一班 engine 渣渣就畫咗個擋水罩希望幫大家<br />\n<br />\n如果各位打算3d print出嚟嘅話 我建議各位用番<strong>粉紅色</strong>或<strong>白色</strong>或<strong>黑色(夜晚作業)</strong> 咁樣就冇咁顯眼唔驚畀人mark低<br />\n<br />\n兩隻都<strong>有分左右</strong>唔好調轉嚟戴o<br />\n<br />\n用6006的各位我建議各位用 p95 particulate filter(3M 5P71),，而唔係用n95(各位要接觸 多過油性煙嘅話呢p95 係好過n95好多)<br />\n60926 STL Download<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!s5hCwYyb!R6KY_WIVD1LrpGftnQ2wY5vPf7LCuwOVUZHVID50e7U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21s5hCwYyb%21R6KY_WIVD1LrpGftnQ2wY5vPf7LCuwOVUZHVID50e7U&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=8fbf5111\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!s5hCwYyb!R6KY_WIVD1LrpGftnQ2wY5vPf7LCuwOVUZHVID50e7U</a><br />\n<br />\n6006 STL Download<br />\n<a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!505HxI4I!TY6PETop-Z1eXYVdMSgCiB0XW_12kHrutiyWSwhtUdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21505HxI4I%21TY6PETop-Z1eXYVdMSgCiB0XW_12kHrutiyWSwhtUdU&d=ly7kxqs2i5dkBMcnx8uly4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=916cb7ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!505HxI4I!TY6PETop-Z1eXYVdMSgCiB0XW_12kHrutiyWSwhtUdU</a><br />\n<br />\n祝大家發個好夢 武運暢通<br />\n<br />\n60926<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pMgY0Ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpMgY0Ff.jpg&h=c9b6c1e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiF69yB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiF69yB.jpg&h=953bffcb&s={SIZE}